definitions.definition: ( Greek mythology ) A child of Asclepius and Epione (or Aristodama ).

main_definition: ( Greek mythology ) A child of Asclepius and Epione (or Aristodama ).

definitions.definition: A member of one of the families that claimed descent from Asclepius , known as physicians or healers.
